Privacy Policy
Last Updated: 21/01/2025
1. Introduction
1.1. This Privacy Policy (hereinafter referred to as the "Policy") explains how Kiski Konstantin (hereinafter referred to as the "Developer") collects, uses, stores, and protects your personal information when you use the mobile application Flow Link (hereinafter referred to as the "App").
2. Information Collection
2.1. Personal Information: We may collect personal information that you voluntarily provide when registering or using the App, including:
Email address
Information related to your Apple ID account for managing subscriptions
2.2. Automatically Collected Information: We automatically collect certain information when you use the App, including:
Device type
Operating system
Device identifiers
Usage data of the App
3. Use of Information
3.1. The collected information is used for the following purposes:
Providing and improving the functionality of the App
Managing subscriptions and payments
Personalizing your experience with the App
Communicating with you regarding support and updates
4. Sharing Information with Third Parties
4.1. We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer your personal information to third parties, except as required by law or necessary to provide services (e.g., payment processing through Apple).
5. Data Security
5.1. We take reasonable measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction.
6. Data Retention
6.1. We retain your personal information only for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this Policy, unless a longer retention period is required or permitted by law.
7. User Rights
7.1. You have the right to:
Request access to your personal information
Correct inaccurate or incomplete information
Request deletion of your personal information
Object to the processing of your information or request restrictions on its use
8. Changes to the Privacy Policy
8.1. We reserve the right to modify this Policy at any time. Changes become effective upon their publication in the App. Continued use of the App after such changes constitutes your acceptance of the updated Policy.
9. Contact Information
If you have any questions or suggestions regarding this Policy, you can contact us at: kostyankiski@gmail.com


